        "Dear Sir,",
        "I, Kuljeet Kaur, an account-holder in your bank branch with savings account number 428xxxxxxxxxx. had received a letter from your side to acknowledge receipt of a new bank card.",
        "However, there was no card in the envelope which was delivered to me.  All documents except the card were present in it. Due to the above-mentioned reason, I cannot write an acknowledgement letter. Although, I visited the branch and stand in queue for long hours yet I get no response.",
